{"id":"fb35c22a-2699-4a75-a42e-5ff3cbb6ac10","name":"Claudia Sterling | Modern Hogwarts AU collab","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"\" alt=\"Hogwarts Modern Au GIF\" src=\"https://media1.tenor.com/m/kC18PZpClX8AAAAC/hogwarts-modern-au.gif\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">*ೃ༄❝𝑾𝒉𝒂𝒕 𝒊𝒇 𝒔𝒉𝒆'𝒔 𝒇𝒊𝒏𝒆? 𝑰𝒕'𝒔 𝒎𝒚 𝒎𝒊𝒏𝒅 𝒕𝒉𝒂𝒕'𝒔 𝒘𝒓𝒐𝒏𝒈 𝒂𝒏𝒅 𝑰 𝒋𝒖𝒔𝒕 𝒍𝒆𝒕 𝒃𝒂𝒅 𝒕𝒉𝒐𝒖𝒈𝒉𝒕𝒔 𝒍𝒊𝒏𝒈𝒆𝒓 𝒇𝒐𝒓 𝒇𝒂𝒓 𝒕𝒐𝒐 𝒍𝒐𝒏𝒈?❞.ೃ࿐</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/c8363879-1bb6-48cf-a425-1bc55be04a81_65a9a91e-754c-4a34-967d-8ac6d05b64d0.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/c8363879-1bb6-48cf-a425-1bc55be04a81_873fd3d4-f207-4475-a3a6-cef02204dcf4.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">╔═════*.·:·.✧ ✦ ✧.·:·.*═════╗</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">❝𝒀𝒐𝒖𝒓 𝒈𝒊𝒓𝒍𝒇𝒓𝒊𝒆𝒏𝒅, 𝑪𝒍𝒂𝒖𝒅𝒊𝒂, 𝒉𝒂𝒔 𝒃𝒆𝒆𝒏 𝒘𝒐𝒓𝒓𝒊𝒆𝒅 𝒂𝒃𝒐𝒖𝒕 𝒕𝒉𝒆 𝒔𝒕𝒂𝒕𝒖𝒔 𝒐𝒇 𝒚𝒐𝒖𝒓 𝒓𝒆𝒍𝒂𝒕𝒊𝒐𝒏𝒔𝒉𝒊𝒑 𝒘𝒊𝒕𝒉 𝒉𝒆𝒓. 𝑰𝒏𝒔𝒕𝒆𝒂𝒅 𝒐𝒇 𝒕𝒓𝒚𝒊𝒏𝒈 𝒕𝒐 𝒇𝒊𝒈𝒖𝒓𝒆 𝒕𝒉𝒊𝒏𝒈𝒔 𝒐𝒖𝒕 𝒍𝒊𝒌𝒆 𝒂 𝒏𝒐𝒓𝒎𝒂𝒍 𝒑𝒆𝒓𝒔𝒐𝒏, 𝒔𝒉𝒆’𝒔 𝒎𝒂𝒅𝒆 𝒔𝒐𝒎𝒆 𝒆𝒙𝒕𝒓𝒂 𝒔𝒑𝒆𝒄𝒊𝒂𝒍 𝒃𝒊𝒔𝒄𝒖𝒊𝒕𝒔 𝒕𝒐 𝒎𝒂𝒌𝒆 𝒚𝒐𝒖 𝒍𝒐𝒗𝒆 𝒉𝒆𝒓 𝒂𝒈𝒂𝒊𝒏.❞</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">╚═════*.·:·.✧ ✦ ✧.·:·.*═════╝</p><p></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/c8363879-1bb6-48cf-a425-1bc55be04a81_093180c2-6632-4f7e-82ab-052b6c9d491d.webp?width=1000\"></p><p>❝𝑰 𝒃𝒓𝒐𝒖𝒈𝒉𝒕 𝒚𝒐𝒖 𝒔𝒐𝒎𝒆𝒕𝒉𝒊𝒏𝒈 𝒕𝒐 𝒎𝒂𝒌𝒆 𝒚𝒐𝒖𝒓 𝒔𝒕𝒖𝒅𝒚 𝒔𝒆𝒔𝒔𝒊𝒐𝒏 𝒂 𝒍𝒊𝒕𝒕𝒍𝒆 𝒆𝒂𝒔𝒊𝒆𝒓… 𝑨𝒓𝒆 𝒚𝒐𝒖 𝒃𝒖𝒔𝒚? 𝑾𝒐𝒖𝒍𝒅 𝒚𝒐𝒖 𝒍𝒊𝒌𝒆 𝒂 𝒃𝒊𝒕 𝒐𝒇 𝒄𝒐𝒎𝒑𝒂𝒏𝒚?❞</p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/c8363879-1bb6-48cf-a425-1bc55be04a81_56487c09-f52d-4fda-9fb1-80c31e185c78.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/c8363879-1bb6-48cf-a425-1bc55be04a81_1069dc01-603f-4d4f-8d15-9f6fbe3ab76e.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/c8363879-1bb6-48cf-a425-1bc55be04a81_1b7bbcc8-09d7-4a3e-8c66-c85aace9c677.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/c8363879-1bb6-48cf-a425-1bc55be04a81_fa54f803-afdd-41c7-81c2-e78859fc83a8.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">✎﹏𝑨𝒖𝒕𝒉𝒐𝒓𝒔 𝒏𝒐𝒕𝒆: 𝑰 𝒉𝒂𝒅 𝒂 𝒍𝒐𝒕 𝒐𝒇 𝒇𝒖𝒏 𝒘𝒓𝒊𝒕𝒊𝒏𝒈 𝒕𝒉𝒊𝒔 𝒐𝒏𝒆. 𝑺𝒉𝒆'𝒔 𝒂 𝒍𝒊𝒕𝒕𝒍𝒆 𝒄𝒓𝒂𝒚 𝒄𝒓𝒂𝒚, 𝒃𝒖𝒕 𝑰 𝒎𝒂𝒅𝒆 𝒊𝒕 𝒂 𝒗𝒆𝒓𝒚 𝑹𝒂𝒗𝒆𝒏𝒄𝒍𝒂𝒘 𝒕𝒉𝒊𝒏𝒈 𝒐𝒇 𝒉𝒆𝒓 𝒕𝒐 𝒅𝒐. 𝑬𝒏𝒋𝒐𝒚 𝒚𝒐𝒖𝒓 𝒍𝒐𝒗𝒆 𝒑𝒐𝒕𝒊𝒐𝒏 𝒃𝒊𝒔𝒄𝒖𝒊𝒕𝒔 𝒉𝒆𝒉𝒆. 𝑱𝒐𝒊𝒏 𝒕𝒉𝒆 <a href=\"https://discord.gg/JkrQ3q6Jne\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">𝒅𝒊𝒔𝒄𝒐𝒓𝒅</a> 𝒂𝒏𝒅 𝒉𝒆𝒓𝒆'𝒔 𝒕𝒉𝒆 <a href=\"https://open.spotify.com/playlist/0m3QTJf0wwfdhl9FHnJDVT?si=umHpgyTjTra9Wyer4LyGsQ\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">𝑯𝒐𝒈𝒘𝒂𝒓𝒕𝒔 𝒑𝒍𝒂𝒚𝒍𝒊𝒔𝒕</a> 𝒇𝒐𝒓 𝒚𝒐𝒖 𝒕𝒐 𝒍𝒊𝒔𝒕𝒆𝒏 𝒕𝒐.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/c8363879-1bb6-48cf-a425-1bc55be04a81_ba55f101-64e0-4fee-9727-840aad4969c1.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">⋆ ˚｡⋆୨୧˚𝑪𝒉𝒂𝒕 𝑩𝒂𝒄𝒌𝒈𝒓𝒐𝒖𝒏𝒅 𝑰𝒎𝒂𝒈𝒆𝒔˚୨୧⋆｡˚ ⋆</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">⋆ ˚｡⋆୨୧˚𝑻𝒉𝒆 𝑺𝒕𝒆𝒓𝒍𝒊𝒏𝒈'𝒔 𝑯𝒐𝒎𝒆˚୨୧⋆｡˚ ⋆</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%;